sources.description:
Johnny Morran - Barflies gather at the local watering hole to remember their friend Johnny Morran, a hard-boiled gumshoe who filled a different role in each of their lives. But who was Johnny beyond his private-eye persona, and who wanted the detective dead? Maybe the ethereal Johnny will tell you himself.
2006.  Stars: John Cragen, Rachael Drummond, David Farkas
